results.name: Denominator(Sum_{i=1..n} 1/i^3)/denominator(Sum_{i=1..n} 1/i).
maple: a := proc(n) local i: denom(add(1/i^3, i = 1 .. n))/denom(add(1/i, i = 1 .. n)): end proc:
program: (PARI) a(n) = denominator(sum(k=1, n, 1/k^3)/sum(k=1, n, 1/k)); \\ _Michel Marcus_, May 07 2020
